    <div class="container">
      <h1>Alaskan Energy Infrastructure</h1>
      <p class="intro-paragraph">Alaskan Energy Infrastructure (AEI) Project is a bold initiative to bring sustainable, community-driven energy solutions to Alaska, including remote regions. Guided by Indigenous insight and real-time collaboration, AEI will deliver actionable policy to the 2026 legislative session.</p>
    </div>

